name: Luca Netz's Dog
description: $BANDIT is a memecoin and ERC-20 token on Abstract Chain based on one of Luca Netz's Dogs named Bandit, Luca Netz is the founder of Abstract Chain. $BANDIT is a memecoin and has no utility or function. $BANDIT was launched on Moonshot Launchpad with Dex Screener. Contract is renounced and Liquidity is burned on the v2 pool. $BANDIT is the top dog coin on Abstract Chain in terms of market cap. $BANDIT is the 4th top memecoin on Abstract Chain in terms of market cap.
